        <DESCRIPTION>The Dark Alin have infected this land, as surely as any disease could ravage a living being. For all the promises made by the Doge, he has done nothing to aid the Alin in their time of need. I will not turn my back on them. We must make the Kalahese safe once more, and to do that, we must destroy all the Dark Alin. If we locate and capture the Dark Alin Capital in this area, their power here will fade to nothing.</DESCRIPTION>
